{"tid":2075793,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅表示，中美貿易協議已經「完結」。","createTime":"2020-06-23T05:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T05:40:52.000Z","uid":306664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2e8b39ee87a273de746f6459b30de27bc0bc54b9","tid":2075793,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:35:02.000Z","msg":"美國白宮貿易顧問納瓦羅表示，中美貿易協議已經「完結」。<br />\n<br />\n納瓦羅接受霍士新聞訪問時表示，中美貿易協議的轉捩點在於中方延誤通報疫情。納瓦羅指，美中雙方在今年1月15日簽署貿易協議後，美方才知道疫情擴散情況。<br />\n<br />\n中美過去先後就疫情、香港等事務問題上導致關係緊張。美國總統特朗普日前認為，自己達成一份非常好的協議，中方正購買很多美國貨，可能會購買總值2500億美元的美國商品。他又承認，推遲制裁打壓新疆維吾爾人的中國官員，是為了避免影響中美貿易協議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533560-20200623.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533560-20200623.htm&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7sv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=be7d3eeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533560-20200623.htm&h=55eb0785\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533560-20200623.htm</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9668649fbbf50e7e683c049ad813452c6f7247","tid":2075793,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T05:40:52.000Z","msg":"壽終正寢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}